<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id6c275197-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e" identifier="/us/usc/t33/s1977"><num value="1977">§ 1977.</num><heading> Termination of authority</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The prize program will terminate after 5 prize competition cycles have been completed.</p>
